this%20story%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BOut%20in%20the%20Lebanon%20mountains%2C%20a%20thistle%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20a%20mighty%20cedar%20tree%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BGive%20your%20daughter%20in%20marriage%20to%20my%20son.%26%23x2019%3B%20But%20just%20then%20a%20wild%20animal%20of%20Lebanon%20came%20by%20and%20stepped%20on%20the%20thistle%2C%20crushing%20it!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_14_10%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20have%20indeed%20defeated%20Edom%2C%20and%20you%20are%20proud%20of%20it.%20But%20be%20content%20with%20your%20victory%20and%20stay%20at%20home!%20Why%20stir%20up%20trouble%20that%20will%20only%20bring%20disaster%20on%20you%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Judah%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_14_11%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Amaziah%20refused%20to%20listen%2C%20so%20King%20Jehoash%20of%20Israel%20mobilized%20his%20army%20against%20King%20Amaziah%20of%20Judah.%20The%20two%20armies%20drew%20up%20their%20battle%20lines%20at%20Beth-shemesh%20in%20Judah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_14_12%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EJudah%20was%20routed%20by%20the%20army%20of%20Israel%2C%20and%20its%20army%20scattered%20and%20fled%20for%20home.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_14_13%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EKing%20Jehoash%20of%20Israel%20captured%20Judah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20king%2C%20Amaziah%20son%20of%20Joash%20and%20grandson%20of%20Ahaziah%2C%20at%20Beth-shemesh.%20Then%20he%20marched%20to%20Jerusalem%2C%20where%20he%20demolished%20600%26%23xA0%3Bfeet%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20clas